blockquote><br />\n有D人身體強壯既就頂得住覺得無問題仲可以發洩到不知幾好<br />\n有D虛弱些少就既明顯出哂問題要戒丁<br />\n<br />\n計我話都係要自己親身驗證過至知<br />\n始終每個人身體狀況都好難講<br />\n<br />\n都係果句<br />\n覺得唔妥既可以試下戒<br />\n話唔定有意想不到既作用<br />\n覺得無問題既 恭喜你 你生活好完滿身體好好 打丁影響唔到你</blockquote><br />\n我試更，不過純粹好想知點解人會咁想打丁"},{"pid":"e8195c3afe9f0335c58f00be2147158587fce516","tid":151992,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:59:56.000Z","msg":"打丁會令男士脫髮、雙目無神、記憶力低、講嘢細聲。唔係話要完全戒，但一日一丁太頻密喇巴打。"},{"pid":"cebffb844129a9971c4adc778627d48e0a9b2fad","tid":151992,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:01:37.000Z","msg":"成功嘅人唔會成日打丁。打丁就好似吸毒咁。"},{"pid":"49d38f058203faf951d97810fca071714bf27242","tid":151992,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:03:57.000Z","msg":"而家啲香港男仔仲細膽過女仔，又細力過女仔，又瘦過女仔，又冇主見過女仔，dse成績又差過女仔，就係打j所致。"},{"pid":"7b9ac68f1c1c8049e21f7a4ee1e9a152ced7689a","tid":151992,"uid":56729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:08:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一日一丁有益定有害<br />\n兩面都有人引用理據去講 <br />\n永遠都無結論</blockquote><br />\n有D人身體強壯既就頂得住覺得無問題仲可以發洩到不知幾好<br />\n有D虛弱些少就既明顯出哂問題要戒丁<br />\n<br />\n計我話都係要自己親身驗證過至知<br />\n始終每個人身體狀況都好難講<br />\n<br />\n都係果句<br />\n覺得唔妥既可以試下戒<br />\n話唔定有意想不到既作用<br />\n覺得無問題既 恭喜你 你生活好完滿身體好好 打丁影響唔到你</blockquote><br />\n我試更，不過純粹好想知點解人會咁想打丁</blockquote><br />\n科學D黎講可以話係行為feedback既一種<br />\n人類既下一步行為某程度上係由上次既feedback去推動<br />\n打丁 -&gt; 覺得好爽 -&gt; (增強左下次想打丁既念頭) -&gt; 打丁既概率高左 -&gt; 繼續打丁/仲打得多左<br />\n<br />\n講遠D<br />\n都可以話係基因驅使我地去咁做<br />\n至於點解就好視乎你既人生哲學宗教信仰<br />\n我自己就覺得打丁係一種加速耗盡生命力去成就下一代既行為<br />\n有D生物 產完一次卵就會死 唔知有無關係? <br />\n佛學有樣野叫著相<br />\n即係比外間既野迷惑誘惑左咁解<br />\n簡單D講<br />\n有淫念/打丁/起貪念等等就係因為你比D外在既野迷惑左<br />\n<br />\n希望解答到你"},{"pid":"9bafac4ee28a51ebfd507c5fc306a7a6b8d1393b","tid":151992,"uid":71143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:13:35.000Z","msg":"3日？！ 大拿拿3日喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講真 我係靠日日打丁先攞滅罪之星<br />\n好多少女因為我打左丁所以幸免於難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主 為左香港治安同女性生命安全著想<br />\n我勸你最好快啲出火 如果唔係我驚你有排坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b036e18e0b2233efd7a2eb2ee03bb361afcf86","tid":151992,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上年先學識打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上係街上或工作環境係完全冇打丁衝動<br />\n但一係屋企對住電腦就即刻有衝勁想丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打丁要學架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好偶然咁學識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da54e6f80021da19bbc8f89eed2cc771bfffd817","tid":151992,"uid":62675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:24:27.000Z","msg":"因為無女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2060b9555c428fa96881978af2efab9dcf680253","tid":151992,"uid":24737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"一見條白滑大腳就想打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪已經無得救了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c6823bfcdf18480820a2be4d950fb9a2fb9b45","tid":151992,"uid":24737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:26:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一見條白滑大<span style=\"color: red;\">腿</span>就想打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪已經無得救了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fd037388cfd83b68dae16eeacd1f9ba6b070173f","tid":151992,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一見條白滑大<span style=\"color: red;\">腿</span>就想打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪已經無得救了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n一日未死都仲有得救<br />\n下定決心既話戒一年都話咁易<br />\n意識到自己有問題係解決問題既關鍵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e487786aa9bf15070b3bfe7f38c1b2f4ed347c0d","tid":151992,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:30:42.000Z","msg":"上網好多誘惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好難自制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48189f5305b4c7a602185ab7ebfe26240d931ab","tid":151992,"uid":73545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:34:21.000Z","msg":"樓主我好明你感受，我以前都一日一丁，<br />\n有時一日三丁都會，一打就七年，<br />\n以前精力好都冇咩問題，<br />\n但上年開始打到記憶力衰退，<br />\n最嚴重既時期連一個鐘前既事都唔記得晒，<br />\n跟住成日想訓教，一日訓十二個鐘都唔夠，<br />\n打打下十足十道友咁，<br />\n見到暴露少少既女圖都打，<br />\n直到同女友搞嘢嗰陣發現好難扯起，<br />\n而且點屌都冇感覺就知出咗事。<br />\n<br />\n依家我戒咗一個月，一想打丁就去跑步，<br />\n跑到冇晒力先停，開頭會成日心思思想打，<br />\n唔打一排就流晒鼻水，十足十啲道友有毒吸咁。<br />\n戒咗一個月條丁開始有好轉，<br />\n不過始終打咗七年，點都唔會復原得晒，<br />\n但至少依家易扯咗，敏感度都恢復返少少。<br />\n<br />\n所以我奉勸大家都係早戒為妙。"},{"pid":"daf581fa3da4f3ac261173b302eafba143148c87","tid":151992,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:35:16.000Z","msg":"之前分完手之後嗰個星期打咗至少三十次飛機<br />\n之前一個月都冇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸，print條女張相出嚟射落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a635e2d93111e251c491c579fd5ee153ca4ca89b","tid":151992,"uid":55194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:35:17.000Z","msg":"我我都差唔多一日一丁<br />\n好想停但條撚控制左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b1d040ac4591ee9b960feee3c6873665c9a0d6","tid":151992,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:52:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前分完手之後嗰個星期打咗至少三十次飛機<br />\n之後一個月都冇打過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸，print條女張相出嚟射落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e356a2265a25316940593e7339ac97f3a0e7d198","tid":151992,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:57:32.000Z","msg":"我宜家冇事冇痛都係一日一丁<br />\n試過三日唔打<br />\n硬到係咁流D前列腺液出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n訓醒又係勁硬<br />\n扯到係咁流汁<br />\n<br />\n試過有一排病左<br />\n半個月都冇心情打<br />\n一病好就硬到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc50811df2eda917b0db2c05ddcd87abdb8c9e1","tid":151992,"uid":68394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:58:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成功嘅人唔會成日打丁。打丁就好似吸毒咁。</blockquote><br />\n成功人士日日屌女更係唔打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ab39e7743674840f9aa9c955e5124900bfa986","tid":151992,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:58:39.000Z","msg":"我係好撚虧 易病多病<br />\n又早射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔做運動<br />\n但真係忍唔住每日一丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n越黎越嚴重 條丁感覺到係差左好多<br />\n要回頭是岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5788635007d1e79fae658967eef01bece10a2ba9","tid":151992,"uid":68394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:59:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打丁會令男士脫髮、雙目無神、記憶力低、講嘢細聲。唔係話要完全戒，但一日一丁太頻密喇巴打。</blockquote><br />\n好驚甩頭髮，我努力戒更"},{"pid":"08355d7c45381412c2decb185f05c650bece9dbf","tid":151992,"uid":68394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T14:00:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家啲香港男仔仲細膽過女仔，又細力過女仔，又瘦過女仔，又冇主見過女仔，dse成績又差過女仔，就係打j所致。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩者有咩關係"},{"pid":"c1e96e90dbe51173c0a169abe904aa76a291199a","tid":151992,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T14:05:18.000Z","msg":"有時做完晒野就更加想打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b64692bb05569ffa19f23e60eb0ac9e935800c","tid":151992,"uid":12265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T14:08:29.000Z","msg":"其實打得會為打以打冇感覺"},{"pid":"d36ea5b81e787cd2f69658066c0689838e42337a","tid":151992,"uid":68394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T14:10:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一日一丁有益定有害<br />\n兩面都有人引用理據去講 <br />\n永遠都無結論</blockquote><br />\n有D人身體強壯既就頂得住覺得無問題仲可以發洩到不知幾好<br />\n有D虛弱些少就既明顯出哂問題要戒丁<br />\n<br />\n計我話都係要自己親身驗證過至知<br />\n始終每個人身體狀況都好難講<br />\n<br />\n都係果句<br />\n覺得唔妥既可以試下戒<br />\n話唔定有意想不到既作用<br />\n覺得無問題既 恭喜你 你生活好完滿身體好好 打丁影響唔到你</blockquote><br />\n我試更，不過純粹好想知點解人會咁想打丁</blockquote><br />\n科學D黎講可以話係行為feedback既一種<br />\n人類既下一步行為某程度上係由上次既feedback去推動<br />\n打丁 -&gt; 覺得好爽 -&gt; (增強左下次想打丁既念頭) -&gt; 打丁既概率高左 -&gt; 繼續打丁/仲打得多左<br />\n<br />\n講遠D<br />\n都可以話係基因驅使我地去咁做<br />\n至於點解就好視乎你既人生哲學宗教信仰<br />\n我自己就覺得打丁係一種加速耗盡生命力去成就下一代既行為<br />\n有D生物 產完一次卵就會死 唔知有無關係? <br />\n佛學有樣野叫著相<br />\n即係比外間既野迷惑誘惑左咁解<br />\n簡單D講<br />\n有淫念/打丁/起貪念等等就係因為你比D外在既野迷惑左<br />\n<br />\n希望解答到你</blockquote><br />\nThx 巴打，之前我記得睇過唔知咩節目話人類係少有一年365日都弱可以交配既物種，你講開行為呢樣野，突然好想知其它動物扑野係咪都好爽，佢地因為爽而家扑野定想繁殖先扑野。<br />\n但有時會無啦啦扯起然後就好想打丁，但扯呢種行為係一種好自然既反應，算唔算無慾望之下打丁。<br />\nSor我好似講到1999"},{"pid":"009f53bb40dccd3a5ab72ec7a52fed296cc020a1","tid":151992,"uid":68394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T14:11:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上年先學識打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上係街上或工作環境係完全冇打丁衝動<br />\n但一係屋企對住電腦就即刻有衝勁想丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打丁要學架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好偶然咁學識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真真係冇咩聽過人學打丁，好細個就自然識"},{"pid":"1be69749894eb02a17b755dbb67611d371481e42","tid":151992,"uid":68394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主我好明你感受，我以前都一日一丁，<br />\n有時一日三丁都會，一打就七年，<br />\n以前精力好都冇咩問題，<br />\n但上年開始打到記憶力衰退，<br />\n最嚴重既時期連一個鐘前既事都唔記得晒，<br />\n跟住成日想訓教，一日訓十二個鐘都唔夠，<br />\n打打下十足十道友咁，<br />\n見到暴露少少既女圖都打，<br />\n直到同女友搞嘢嗰陣發現好難扯起，<br />\n而且點屌都冇感覺就知出咗事。<br />\n<br />\n依家我戒咗一個月，一想打丁就去跑步，<br />\n跑到冇晒力先停，開頭會成日心思思想打，<br />\n唔打一排就流晒鼻水，十足十啲道友有毒吸咁。<br />\n戒咗一個月條丁開始有好轉，<br />\n不過始終打咗七年，點都唔會復原得晒，<br />\n但至少依家易扯咗，敏感度都恢復返少少。<br />\n<br />\n所以我奉勸大家都係早戒為妙。</blockquote><br />\n戒緊了，但有時又會諗積積埋埋唔打會虧咁好易射"}]}